      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">How much does Hestan appliance repair cost in Los Angeles?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">Most Hestan repairs run $145–$620. Trellis Burner service, Horizon Hood spring, or LED lighting work is on the lower end. Campania igniter, valve replacement, or control board runs higher. Diagnostic fee is $89, waived when you proceed. Written flat-rate estimate before work begins.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">Do you repair the Hestan Campania Pizza Oven?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes — and this is a specialty. The Campania operates at 700°F, which creates service requirements completely unlike a standard grill. We use OEM Hestan Campania high-temp igniters specifically rated for this temperature environment. Standard grill igniters fail rapidly at Campania temperatures — using the wrong part is the most common reason a recent Campania repair fails again quickly.</div>
      </div>
